metadata.name: k0mp0s1t #1
metadata.description:
K0mp0s1t gains creative inspiration from an eclectic variety of art forms, movements, techniques and styles.
 African art, abstract art, surrealism, sci-fi and other genres greatly influence the essence of this collection.
They are created using a combination of mixed media, digital drawings and artificial intelligence, resulting in bizarre, unique and colorful one of a kind artworks.
A k0mp0s1t represents the natural imperfect human tendencies we all have.
 At times we can be ugly, unbalanced and a little weird, but we accept it within ourselves and with others.
 At the end of the day we should embrace the fact that we are all still beautiful, passionate and unique in our own special way.
